highlights.text: Ultra Bra has the most spots on Viral Songs Finland. “Minä Suojelen Sinua Kaikelta” is the highest at #13.
“Korjaa mut” by koira is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Finland, up 32 spots at #32.
“Mun ihminen” by ELLIMEI has been on Viral Songs Finland the longest, at 121 days straight.
“Montagem Supersonic” by KHAOS and Jmilton is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Finland at #69.
